    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm looking at some budget stuff for my shop. i'm located in a pretty rural area where everything is way cheaper than in the city. if the state minimum wage goes up again, how is that usually gonna hit small businesses like mine? just trying to get a sense of the impact.",
